  "texts": [
    "This will help in gaining a deeper, more analytical understanding of the topic.\"",
    "Data Collection and AI ResponsesAI responses to the posed questions were systematically collected and formatted for analysis.",
    "This phase involved the curation of raw data to conform to the requirements for constructing knowledge graphs.",
    "This resulted in a 50 x 3 answers matrix.",
    "Expert EvaluationA panel of two marine and coastal ecosystem experts (two authors, LK and ED, in this paper) assessed the AI responses and scored each question prompt on accuracy, relevance, depth, creativity, and semantic clarity using a scale of 1-5 (1 being worst and 5 being the best)."
